data.description: Looking for a move-in ready home? Enjoy sitting on the covered front porch in this quiet neighborhood. This 4-bedroom 2-bath home has been quality remodeled from top to bottom!  New roof, vinyl insulated windows, new vinyl siding, original hard wood floors restored to their natural beauty, new flooring in kitchen and baths, all new bath fixtures and additional full bath added in finished basement, mud room, partially fenced back yard. Plenty of storage space including one cedar lined closet. Conveniently located near the Dayton Mall, plenty of restaurants, I-75 and I-675.  Won't last long!  Please Wear provided booties when entering.
